author: itv.com
title: Liberation service set to return to normal
text:
Ferry services to and from the Channel Islands are expected to return to normal today.
It is the first scheduled sailing of the Condor Liberation since Friday.
Disruption for passengers began when the Liberation was cancelled over the weekend because of problems with the exhaust system.
Cancellations continued yesterday as emergency repairs were completed.
